                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d364">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Dawson</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Bogota</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1909-02-23">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 23, 1909</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The treaties passed reading to-day. The proceedings public. The treaties now are
                    before a special committee. No unfavorable developments so far.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Dawson.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
